This repository contains application code and documentation for ASR,
dictionary search, Lemko-to-Polish translation assistance, phonemization,
transliteration, and StyleTTS2-based text-to-speech workflows.

The repository does not include the production database, private logs, voice
reference recordings, FastText model binaries, NeMo model weights, StyleTTS2
weights, OpenAI credentials, or deployment secrets. These assets may have
separate owners, licenses, privacy obligations, and usage restrictions.

Third-party dependencies are listed in requirements-prod.txt and summarized in
THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.md. Their copyrights, licenses, and notices remain with
their respective owners.

Model and data governance notes are documented in:

- MODELS.md
- DATA_LICENSE.md
- PRIVACY.md
- SECURITY.md
